THURSDAY , APRIL 11 , 2013 , 12 : 12 AM Two accused gangbangers went on trial Wednesday for tragically killing a mother of 12 as they were spraying bullets from a Brooklyn rooftop . "Zurana Horton became a victim of the senseless gang violence that plagues Brooklyn , " prosecutor Seth Goldman said at the start of the murder trial of half - brothers Andrew Lopez , 20 , and Jonathan Carrasquillo , 24 . The 34 - year - old mother was struck in the chest from a bullet that ricocheted off a fence in her Brownsville neighborhood in Oct . 2011 , authorities said . Lopez was allegedly targeting members of the Young Goon gang , who had a seven - year beef with the 8 Block crew he belonged to .
